dataset.title: New findings of Prototherium ausetanum (Mammalia, Pan-Sirenia) from paving stones in Girona (Catalonia, Spain)?

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Voss, Manja, Hampe, Oliver, Mahlow, Kristin, Vilanova, Joan C. (2023): New findings of Prototherium ausetanum (Mammalia, Pan-Sirenia) from paving stones in Girona (Catalonia, Spain)?
